channel.title: Skills IDs
channel.description:
Can somebody please post a list of which skill ID equals which, I just CBF to do the research myself, and it would be much appreciated if somebody put it in an [tt]enum[/tt] format (though not required).
If you don't know what I mean by skills IDs, then I mean like playerXP[1] is the player's attack XP, etc.
This will speed up development of the BeanServ project.
Thank you, ~io9
